# This repository tracks the dilijanvillas WordPress theme only.
#
# The working directory also holds ~11 GB that must never reach GitHub:
# full site backups ("Old wp from domen"), raw photo/video downloads,
# WordPress core, and database dumps containing real customer data.
# So everything is excluded by default and the theme is added back explicitly.

/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md

!/wordpress/
/wordpress/*
!/wordpress/wp-content/
/wordpress/wp-content/*
!/wordpress/wp-content/themes/
/wordpress/wp-content/themes/*
!/wordpress/wp-content/themes/dilijanvillas/

# Source video stays out of git — it belongs in the WordPress media library.
/wordpress/wp-content/themes/dilijanvillas/videos/

# Local secrets / deploy credentials. Redundant against the catch-all above,
# kept explicit so loosening that rule cannot leak them by accident.
.vscode/sftp.json
.vscode/sftp.json.local
wp-config.php
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Editor / OS noise.
.history/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
node_modules/
